    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>悬念</strong> — <strong>个在“无尽的锈墙”中被生活重担折磨的人的第一人称恐怖游戏</strong>。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325530/extras/b62247895ae547c3734c56b5cf35e076.poster.avif?t=1762512230\" width=600 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325530/extras/b62247895ae547c3734c56b5cf35e076.webm?t=1762512230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325530/extras/b62247895ae547c3734c56b5cf35e076.mp4?t=1762512230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>故事</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >过去如何已不重要，未来无法生活，但显然现在是一种折磨。每天，主角和他的导师都按照相同的日程生活。他们努力工作于一个与人工智能相关的神秘项目。此外，机器持续且激进的控制可能会压垮任何人的意识，如果你无法应对—最好不要知道会发生什么。如此多的问题，却如此少的答案。是时候对此采取行动了。。。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索一个可怕的替代未来，克服挑战，或者你会被救（或至少了解一丝真相）。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏性</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>简单的游戏玩法，包括行走模拟器、解谜和平台跳跃等类型</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>与周围的世界互动</strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>简洁的用户界面</strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>使用各种方法解决任务并完成游戏</strong></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏功能</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>令人沮丧的孤独和孤立感， 无助和偏执的气氛</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>各种不同的谜题</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PSX风格的图像 + 新的渲染元素（视差纹理、体积雾等）</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>原创音轨</strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>平均游戏时间：1小时15分钟</strong></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>添加到愿望清单!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325530/extras/6126b590cfcefde4faf0af7839618da7.poster.avif?t=1762512230\" width=600 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325530/extras/6126b590cfcefde4faf0af7839618da7.webm?t=1762512230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325530/extras/6126b590cfcefde4faf0af7839618da7.mp4?t=1762512230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
